Module de.sft.dlt
Package de.s42.dlt.parser.antlr

Class DLTParserBaseListener

java.lang.Object
de.s42.dlt.parser.antlr.DLTParserBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
DLTParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
TemplateCompiler.ParserListener
public class DLTParserBaseListener extends Object implements DLTParserListener
This class provides an empty implementation of DLTParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
